OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1780369437
OL,3,C'I never thought I'd be scared to be a
OL,4,CJew': ITV News report from Golders
OL,5,CGreen
OL,7,FWarning: This article contains
OL,8,Fdistressing content
OL,10,FWords by ITV News Reporter Sam Holder
OL,11,Fand ITV News Senior Producer Georgia
OL,12,FZiebart
OL,14,FWe are 20 minutes into our lunch with
OL,15,Fthe Jewish neighbourhood security
OL,16,Fforce Shomrim when one of the
OL,17,Fvolunteers' phones starts to ring.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/33
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
