PN,31102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1780369437
OL,3,C'I never thought I'd be scared to be a
OL,4,CJew': ITV News report from Golders
OL,5,CGreen
OL,7,FIt is coordinator Ben's teenage
OL,8,Fdaughter. She is on a bus with friends
OL,9,Fjust minutes away from where we are in
OL,10,FGolders Green, and passengers are
OL,11,Fhurling antisemitic abuse at them, she
OL,12,Fsays.
OL,14,FWithin seconds, Ben and the other
OL,15,Fvolunteers jump into action, abruptly
OL,16,Fleaving the restaurant and heading
OL,17,Ftowards the bus route in the Shomrim
OL,18,Fpatrol car.
OL,20,FThe timing feels strikingly
OL,21,Fsignificant.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/33
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
