OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1780369437
OL,3,C'I never thought I'd be scared to be a
OL,4,CJew': ITV News report from Golders
OL,5,CGreen
OL,7,FSitting in a Kosher restaurant on
OL,8,FGolders Green high street, we had been
OL,9,Fdiscussing the extent to which
OL,10,Fsecurity concerns and antisemitic
OL,11,Fincidents have become part of everyday
OL,12,Flife for many British Jews.
OL,14,FGolders Green is one of the country's
OL,15,Fmost visibly Jewish neighbourhoods,
OL,16,Fand in recent months, it has become a
OL,17,Ffocal point for questions around
OL,18,Fsafety, belonging and identity.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/33
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1780369437
OL,3,C'I never thought I'd be scared to be a
OL,4,CJew': ITV News report from Golders
OL,5,CGreen
OL,7,FJewish life is woven into the high
OL,8,Fstreet, which is lined with Kosher
OL,9,Fbakeries, Hebrew bookshops, and
OL,10,Fmakeshift synagogues. Strung above
OL,11,Fthem are Union Jack flags, a visible
OL,12,Fexpression of a community that is
OL,13,Fproud not only to be Jewish, but
OL,14,FBritish too.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/33
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1780369437
OL,3,C'I never thought I'd be scared to be a
OL,4,CJew': ITV News report from Golders
OL,5,CGreen
OL,7,FIt was on this same high street that,
OL,8,Fin April, two Jewish men ` Shloime
OL,9,FRand and Moshe Shine ` were stabbed in
OL,10,Fan alleged terrorist attack. There has
OL,11,Falso been a spate of arson attacks in
OL,12,Fthe area, including against the Jewish-
OL,13,Fled ambulance service, Hatzola.
OL,15,FBen, who has volunteered with Shomrim
OL,16,Ffor more than a decade, was among the
OL,17,Ffirst on the scene after the attack in
OL,18,FApril.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/33
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1780369437
OL,3,C'I never thought I'd be scared to be a
OL,4,CJew': ITV News report from Golders
OL,5,CGreen
OL,7,F"We're proud Jews, we're proud that
OL,8,Fwe're part of this society, and we
OL,9,Fgive a lot to society, but we don't
OL,10,Ffeel safe," he tells ITV News.
OL,12,FThe feeling is not uncommon among Jews
OL,13,Fliving in the UK.
OL,15,FMany feel that the events since
OL,16,FOctober 7 have made everyday life feel
OL,17,Fpolitically charged, and visible
OL,18,FJewish signifiers like wearing a
OL,19,Fkippah or speaking Hebrew have left
OL,20,Fthem feeling exposed to hostility.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/33
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1780369437
OL,3,C'I never thought I'd be scared to be a
OL,4,CJew': ITV News report from Golders
OL,5,CGreen
OL,7,FBut many British Jews feel they are
OL,8,Fheld personally responsible for the
OL,9,Factions of the Israeli state, simply
OL,10,Fbecause they are visibly Jewish ` and
OL,11,Fsay they have suffered antisemitic
OL,12,Fabuse as a result.
OL,14,F"If I walk to the Science Museum with
OL,15,Fmy son, I'll have someone call out
OL,16,F'Free Palestine' to me because he sees
OL,17,Fmy kippah on my head," says Ben's
OL,18,Ffellow Shomrim volunteer, David.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/33
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1780369437
OL,3,C'I never thought I'd be scared to be a
OL,4,CJew': ITV News report from Golders
OL,5,CGreen
OL,7,F"What's that supposed to mean to me as
OL,8,Fa British Jew living here, walking
OL,9,Fwith my child, trying to exercise
OL,10,Ffreedom. What are you going to do
OL,11,Fnext? Are you going to attack me? Are
OL,12,Fyou going to punch me?"
OL,14,FShortly after they leave the
OL,15,Frestaurant, we catch up with Ben and
OL,16,Fthe other Shomrim volunteers, who have
OL,17,Fapprehended a group of five suspects.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/33
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1780369437
OL,3,C'I never thought I'd be scared to be a
OL,4,CJew': ITV News report from Golders
OL,5,CGreen
OL,7,FBen's daughter and her friends say
OL,8,Fthey were on their way to a nearby
OL,9,Fshopping centre when a group of boys
OL,10,Fbegan shouting "Adolf Hitler" and
OL,11,Fperforming Nazi salutes at them.
OL,13,FThe girls say one of the boys had
OL,14,Fshouted: "Hitler didn't manage to get
OL,15,Fyou, but we will."
OL,17,FBen and his colleagues contacted the
OL,18,Fpolice, who attended almost
OL,19,Fimmediately.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/33
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1780369437
OL,3,C'I never thought I'd be scared to be a
OL,4,CJew': ITV News report from Golders
OL,5,CGreen
OL,7,FThe problem, Ben tells us, is not with
OL,8,Fpolice presence, but prosecution. He
OL,9,Fsays there have been multiple examples
OL,10,Fof antisemitic attacks which have been
OL,11,Fleft without arrests, or else trials
OL,12,Fwhich have not ended in prison
OL,13,Fsentences, often on mental health
OL,14,Fgrounds.
OL,16,FIn this case, there is frustration
OL,17,Ffrom Shomrim when the police say they
OL,18,Fare unable to arrest the suspects on
OL,19,Fthe scene because they are underage.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/33
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31111
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1780369437
OL,3,C'I never thought I'd be scared to be a
OL,4,CJew': ITV News report from Golders
OL,5,CGreen
OL,7,F"We need action. This cannot go on,"
OL,8,Fwe hear Ben tell the police. "Our
OL,9,Fkids, 13-year-old girls, cannot go to
OL,10,Fthe shops without receiving a Nazi
OL,11,Fsalute."
OL,13,F"We want to enforce the full force of
OL,14,Fthe law, because warnings are not
OL,15,Fenough anymore," he says. "Nothing's
OL,16,Fgoing to be prosecuted, so why should
OL,17,FI feel safe?"
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/33
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31112
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1780369437
OL,3,C'I never thought I'd be scared to be a
OL,4,CJew': ITV News report from Golders
OL,5,CGreen
OL,7,FWe follow Ben and the other Shomrim
OL,8,Fvolunteers back to his house in
OL,9,FGolders Green, where the police have
OL,10,Fcome to take statements from his
OL,11,Fdaughter and her friends.
OL,13,FIn the hour since we have left the
OL,14,Frestaurant, the team has already been
OL,15,Fcalled out to three separate
OL,16,Fantisemitic incidents in the area. Ben
OL,17,Fhas been so busy, he says, that his
OL,18,FShomrim radio battery has already died.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/33
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31113
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1780369437
OL,3,C'I never thought I'd be scared to be a
OL,4,CJew': ITV News report from Golders
OL,5,CGreen
OL,7,F"To feel that everyone was on the bus
OL,8,Fand no one did anything, it just felt
OL,9,Funsafe," Ben's daughter says. "It's
OL,10,Fgot to the point where people are not
OL,11,Fashamed to do it in front of everyone
OL,12,Fpublicly, just shouting at us as if
OL,13,Fit's okay."
OL,15,F"It just makes you feel less like
OL,16,Fthere's a future for Jews in London
OL,17,Fand maybe I'll be better off somewhere
OL,18,Felse."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/33
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31114
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1780369437
OL,3,C'I never thought I'd be scared to be a
OL,4,CJew': ITV News report from Golders
OL,5,CGreen
OL,7,FThe Met Police said officers had
OL,8,Fdetained five boys, aged between 12
OL,9,Fand 15, in the wake of the incident.
OL,10,FNo arrests have been made, they said,
OL,11,Fbut enquiries continued.
OL,13,FIn a statement, the force said they
OL,14,F"understand that concerns remain high
OL,15,Fwithin Jewish communities and are
OL,16,F"focusing resources around vulnerable
OL,17,Fareas to protect communities, disrupt
OL,18,Foffenders and tackle crime".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/33
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31115
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1780369437
OL,3,C'I never thought I'd be scared to be a
OL,4,CJew': ITV News report from Golders
OL,5,CGreen
OL,7,FJust hours after we've finished
OL,8,Ffilming for the day, there is yet
OL,9,Fanother antisemitic attack in Golders
OL,10,FGreen.
OL,12,FShalev, 22, is speaking in Hebrew on
OL,13,Fthe phone late on Sunday night, when
OL,14,Fhe says five masked men physically
OL,15,Fattacked him, shouting: "Inta Yehudi"
OL,16,F` 'are you Jewish?', in Arabic.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/33
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31116
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1780369437
OL,3,C'I never thought I'd be scared to be a
OL,4,CJew': ITV News report from Golders
OL,5,CGreen
OL,7,F"They dragged me to the floor and they
OL,8,Fkicked my face, my hands," Shalev
OL,9,Ftells us two days later, the scabs and
OL,10,Fbruises from the attack still visible
OL,11,Fon his face.
OL,13,F"I just closed my eyes and tried to
OL,14,Fdefend myself. I just hoped they
OL,15,Fdidn't have a knife. I just hoped they
OL,16,Fweren't going to kill me."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/33
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31117
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1780369437
OL,3,C'I never thought I'd be scared to be a
OL,4,CJew': ITV News report from Golders
OL,5,CGreen
OL,7,FShalev, who lives in Israel, was
OL,8,Fvisiting his family in Golders Green.
OL,9,FHe has visited the area many times,
OL,10,Fand says he's noticed a marked
OL,11,Fincrease in antisemitism in the last
OL,12,Ffew years.
OL,14,F"Why would people go in masks and
OL,15,Fhoodies at 2am to the heart of the
OL,16,FJewish area? They wanted to find
OL,17,Fsomeone like me," he says. "It felt
OL,18,Flike I was in Europe in the 1940s. It
OL,19,Ffelt like the dark times."
OL,26,@vD@AOUyD@QO]yD@\OU{D@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/33
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31118
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1780369437
OL,3,C'I never thought I'd be scared to be a
OL,4,CJew': ITV News report from Golders
OL,5,CGreen
OL,7,F"Golders Green has always been the
OL,8,Fcentral hub of Jewish life in London,"
OL,9,FShalev's friend, Tilly, adds. "It felt
OL,10,Flike the one place where you can
OL,11,Falways be visibly Jewish, where you
OL,12,Ffeel the most safe.
OL,14,F"Where is the safest place in London
OL,15,Fto be Jewish if it's not Golders
OL,16,FGreen? It's terrifying."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/33
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31119
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1780369437
OL,3,C'I never thought I'd be scared to be a
OL,4,CJew': ITV News report from Golders
OL,5,CGreen
OL,7,FIt is a feeling echoed by many Jews in
OL,8,FLondon. An increasing number of
OL,9,Ffamilies, many of whom have lived in
OL,10,Fthe area for generations, feel they
OL,11,Fhave no choice but to leave.
OL,13,FOur final visit in Golders Green is to
OL,14,FBaruch, who, along with his wife
OL,15,FDaniella, is packing up their home
OL,16,Fahead of moving to Israel.
OL,18,FBaruch is an NHS doctor, working in a
OL,19,FLondon hospital. But increasingly, he
OL,20,Ffeels there is no future for his young
OL,21,Ffamily in the UK.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G19/33
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31120
SC,0020
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1780369437
OL,3,C'I never thought I'd be scared to be a
OL,4,CJew': ITV News report from Golders
OL,5,CGreen
OL,7,FBaruch tells us his ancestors have
OL,8,Flived in England since the time of
OL,9,FOliver Cromwell. Now, he is the last
OL,10,Fmember of his family left in the
OL,11,Fcountry - his parents and five sisters
OL,12,Fhaving already moved to Israel.
OL,14,F"To have that long lineage of a family
OL,15,Fwho came here 400 years ago and now
OL,16,Fhaving to leave because on the one
OL,17,Fhand we want to leave, we love Israel,
OL,18,Fbut also leaving because of
OL,19,Fantisemitism, is very sad."
OL,26,@vD@AOU{D@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G20/33
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
