OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1780369437
OL,3,C'I never thought I'd be scared to be a
OL,4,CJew': ITV News report from Golders
OL,5,CGreen
OL,7,FThe family previously lived in
OL,8,FManchester, and Baruch had been at a
OL,9,Fneighbouring synagogue when two Jewish
OL,10,Fmen were killed in the Heaton Park
OL,11,Fsynagogue attack. They moved back to
OL,12,Fthe north London community where
OL,13,FBaruch and Daniella grew up in January
OL,14,Fthis year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G21/33
