OL,3,C'I never thought I'd be scared to be a
OL,4,CJew': ITV News report from Golders
OL,5,CGreen
OL,7,FFor many Jewish people, moving to
OL,8,FIsrael ` known as making Aliyah ` is
OL,9,Frooted in faith and a desire to build
OL,10,Fa life in the Jewish homeland. But
OL,11,Fincreasingly, families feel their
OL,12,Fdecision is also being shaped by a
OL,13,Fgrowing feeling that there is no
OL,14,Ffuture for Jews in Britain.
OL,16,F"On the outside, it might seem weird
OL,17,Fthat you'd want to move to a war
OL,18,Fzone," Daniella admits, "But people in
OL,19,FIsrael worry about us. They ask us,
OL,20,Fhow are we coping with the
OL,21,Fantisemitism?"
OL,26,@xD@AOUzD@FO]zD@YOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G22/33
