OL,3,C'I never thought I'd be scared to be a
OL,4,CJew': ITV News report from Golders
OL,5,CGreen
OL,7,FBaruch says he regularly gets shouted
OL,8,Fat in the street when wearing his
OL,9,Fkippah, and has been told to "go back
OL,10,Fto where he came from." Once, in
OL,11,FManchester, someone in a passing car
OL,12,Fthreatened to throw acid at his face
OL,13,Fsimply because he was visibly Jewish.
OL,15,FHe also says he's experienced
OL,16,Fantisemitism within the NHS and in his
OL,17,Fwork as a doctor, ranging from other
OL,18,Fdoctors refusing to treat patients who
OL,19,Fhave Israel on their birth
OL,20,Fcertificate, to refusing to give
OL,21,FJewish patients kosher meals.
OL,26,@qD@^OUrD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G23/33
