OL,3,C'I never thought I'd be scared to be a
OL,4,CJew': ITV News report from Golders
OL,5,CGreen
OL,7,FThe Department of Health said the
OL,8,Freports were shocking and that an
OL,9,F"urgent review" into antisemitism and
OL,10,Fracism in the health service had been
OL,11,Fcommissioned.
OL,13,FFor many of the people we've spoken to
OL,14,Fin Golders Green, the question is no
OL,15,Flonger whether antisemitism exists in
OL,16,FBritain, but why it has become so
OL,17,Fnormalised.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G24/33
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
