OL,3,C'I never thought I'd be scared to be a
OL,4,CJew': ITV News report from Golders
OL,5,CGreen
OL,7,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FA Metropolitan Police spokesperson
OL,13,Fsaid: "Police were called at 14.42hrs
OL,14,Fon Sunday, 17 May following reports
OL,15,Fthat a group of girls, aged between 14
OL,16,Fand 15, had been subjected to
OL,17,Fantisemitic abuse on a bus nearby to
OL,18,FBrent Cross Shopping Centre.
OL,26,@uD@GOU
