OL,3,C'I never thought I'd be scared to be a
OL,4,CJew': ITV News report from Golders
OL,5,CGreen
OL,7,F"Working alongside the community group
OL,8,FShomrim to identify the suspects, Met
OL,9,Fofficers detained five boys, aged
OL,10,Fbetween 12 and 15.
OL,12,F"There have been no arrests and
OL,13,Fenquiries continue. Appointments will
OL,14,Fbe made for the boys to speak with
OL,15,Fofficers within the new Community
OL,16,FProtection Team, who are dedicated to
OL,17,Finvestigating hate crime incidents.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G27/33
