OL,3,C'I never thought I'd be scared to be a
OL,4,CJew': ITV News report from Golders
OL,5,CGreen
OL,7,F"We understand that concerns remain
OL,8,Fhigh within Jewish communities. We
OL,9,Fcontinue to have an enhanced policing
OL,10,Fplan which focuses our resource around
OL,11,Fvulnerable areas to protect
OL,12,Fcommunities, disrupt offenders and
OL,13,Ftackle crime."
OL,15,FA Crown Prosecution Service
OL,16,Fspokesperson said: "Antisemitism has
OL,17,Fno place in our society, and we are
OL,18,Fdetermined to help combat the
OL,19,Fincreasing levels of hate crime.
OL,26,@uD@NO]xD@TOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G28/33
