OL,3,C'I never thought I'd be scared to be a
OL,4,CJew': ITV News report from Golders
OL,5,CGreen
OL,7,F"We continue to work closely with
OL,8,Fpolice to ensure cases are reviewed
OL,9,Fpromptly and, where appropriate,
OL,10,Fbrought before the courts as quickly
OL,11,Fas possible.
OL,13,F"We continue to engage directly with
OL,14,FJewish communities to ensure their
OL,15,Fvoices are heard and concerns
OL,16,Faddressed.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G29/33
