OL,3,C'I never thought I'd be scared to be a
OL,4,CJew': ITV News report from Golders
OL,5,CGreen
OL,7,F"Anyone who has experienced or
OL,8,Fwitnessed antisemitic abuse or
OL,9,Fviolence is encouraged to report it to
OL,10,Fthe police. Reporting is vital in
OL,11,Fhelping us work with policing partners
OL,12,Fto take action and bring offenders to
OL,13,Fjustice."
OL,15,FA Department of Health and Social Care
OL,16,Fspokesperson said: "These reports are
OL,17,Fshocking. It is unacceptable that
OL,18,Fpeople do not currently feel safe
OL,19,Fworking in and using the health
OL,20,Fservice.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@IO]xD@TOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G30/33
