OL,3,C'I never thought I'd be scared to be a
OL,4,CJew': ITV News report from Golders
OL,5,CGreen
OL,7,F"Recent incidents of antisemitism have
OL,8,Fdrawn stark attention to problems of
OL,9,Fculture and how racist incidents are
OL,10,Faddressed.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G31/33
