OL,3,C'I never thought I'd be scared to be a
OL,4,CJew': ITV News report from Golders
OL,5,CGreen
OL,7,F"This government has been clear that
OL,8,Fchange is needed and that the medical
OL,9,Fhealthcare professional regulatory
OL,10,Fsystem is failing to protect Jewish
OL,11,Fpatients and NHS staff. That's why the
OL,12,Fprime minister ordered an urgent
OL,13,Freview, led by Lord Mann, into
OL,14,Fantisemitism and all forms of racism
OL,15,Fin the health service. We will use
OL,16,Fevery tool at our disposal to make
OL,17,Fsure Jewish NHS staff feel safe at
OL,18,Fwork."
OL,26,@oD@AOUzD@FO]
